{"id": "23700", "post": "<div class=\"post-23700 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-faq\" id=\"post-23700\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/frequently-asked-questions-virtual-private-servers-explained/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Frequently Asked Questions: Virtual Private Servers Explained</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/faq/\" rel=\"tag\">faq</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> June 22, 2020 @ 12:32 pm, by Jon Biloh</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/VPS-FAQ.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" title=\"Frequently Asked Questions: Virtual Private Servers Explained\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/VPS-FAQ.jpg.webp\" alt=\"Frequently Asked Questions: Virtual Private Servers Explained\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> There are lots of questions about Virtual Private Servers (VPS), from the basics, like what they are and what advantages do they offer to more detailed questions about hypervisors and what underlying technologies are best for each use case.</p><p>We\u2019ve <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/virtual-private-server-frequently-asked-questions-vps-faq/\">recently published a fairly extensive starters guide</a> that aims to answers the most common questions about Virtual Private Servers. So, before you get started shopping for a <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\">cheap linux vps</a> , <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/windows/\">cheap windows vps</a> or <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/windows/\">cheap dedicated server</a> be sure to check the guide out first.</p><p>Also available to help those just getting started is a <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/frequently-asked-questions-los-angeles-vps/\">recently published article</a> that answers frequently asked questions pertaining to virtual private server hosting in Los Angeles, California, which is an informative read.</p><p>As always we welcome feedback in the comment section below.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Ffrequently-asked-questions-virtual-private-servers-explained%2F&amp;t=Frequently%20Asked%20Questions%3A%20Virtual%20Private%20Servers%20Explained\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Frequently%20Asked%20Questions%3A%20Virtual%20Private%20Servers%20Explained&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Ffrequently-asked-questions-virtual-private-servers-explained%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Ffrequently-asked-questions-virtual-p